<br>
The real problem is, when we got nerfed, initially, everyone noticed it, and it's been downhill ever since.  I give you this scenario... How many times, when someone is contemplating accepting you into a group do you get this, &quot;How much does your best DD do?&quot;  I get this all the time.  Then ultimately, &quot;Oh, well, we're full right now, maybe next time.&quot;<br>
<br>
Yeah, OK.  Thanks for considering me for the nanosecond it took you to find a chanter/cleric/tank.  <br>
