They had problems post 50, but everyone jumped on the bandwagon and suddenly rangers always sucked for every level.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umarktodd.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MarkTodd</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/15/01 6:18:49 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: It's all our own fault</span><hr size=1> Wow, I guess Verant has nothing to do with this whole process? <br>
